TopicTitle: Stratzenblitz75 is back! Check out his streams

Articles.Content:
Hello fellas

Some of you might've heard the name Stratzenblitz75. For those who haven't: he's a KSP YouTuber attempting outrageous challenges and builds. He has uploaded many videos on KSP (multiple of them reaching millions of views individually), and they are definitely worth checking out

Stratzenblitz has been inactive on the Youtube for over a year, with his last appearance in April 2023. However, now he has reappeared, and he's currently streaming a very ambitious mission, landing a hilariously huge spaceplane in... well, I won't spoil it since he ain't spoiling it in his own thumbnail, so check it out for yourselves! He's streaming the Part 2 currently, but considering the mission there will probably be other parts coming up, so if you miss this stream you might catch another one
Oo yeah I love his videos!
